She's just a mere concubine.

30
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:24,839
She's not capable of anything.

31
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,039
You should get some rest.

32
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,960
Your Highness is right.

33
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,000
She's but a concubine.

34
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,880
In this world,

35
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:36,199
there are many who
don't know their places.

36
