39
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:45,360
she's going to covet after
the position as the first wife.

40
00:02:45,679 --> 00:02:46,880
Who knows?

41
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,360
You're right, Zhu Momo.

42
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,839
She will not get what she wants.

43
