Continue the learning tomorrow.

44
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,880
Continue.

45
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,479
Did you manage to figure something out?

46
00:03:15,839 --> 00:03:16,720
Yes.

47
