I'm going to check on her.

62
00:03:44,119 --> 00:03:44,600
All right.

63
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,240
Hanchen.

64
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,800
Although we owe Xiaoman big time,

65
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,520
you need to bear a sense of propriety.

66
00:03:52,839 --> 00:03:53,360
You mustn't

67
