treat her like the first wife.

68
00:03:55,399 --> 00:03:57,119
If such a hope is evoked in her,

69
00:03:57,399 --> 00:03:58,559
it's only going to harm her.

70
00:04:00,479 --> 00:04:01,199
There are things

71
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,759
I owe her.

72
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,559
