82
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:48,760
Your hands.

83
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,480
Did you come just to do this?

84
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:03,640
Yes.

85
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,600
You're such a fool.

86
