90
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,279
Why should I compromise?

91
00:05:14,519 --> 00:05:15,440
Did you know

92
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,480
for married women to return
to the academy,

93
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:18,920
they'd turn into a laughing stock?

94
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,200
A laughing stock?

95
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,920
Pursuing studies will be made a joke,

96
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:26,679
but attending to
trivial matters of the house

97
00:05:26,679 --> 00:05:27,880
is more important?

98
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:30,320
Both of us are married by contract.

99
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:31,399
After two years,

100
