we no longer have anything
to do with each other.

101
00:05:33,799 --> 00:05:35,359
If I'm not concerned of
my future right now,

102
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,079
after two years,

103
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,839
do you want me to end up

104
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:40,559
from one backyard to another?

105
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,839
We shall go our own ways
after two years?

106
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:47,959
Fine.

107
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:49,880
Forget about the academy.

108
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,320
You...

109
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,239
Wick was right.

110
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,760
The moment you can rely on a man

111
00:05:57,200 --> 00:05:58,600
is when sows are able to climb trees.

112
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:39,940
(Qu Yuan's Poem)

113
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,600
Congwen.

114
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,760
What are you doing here?

115
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,519
You're dismissed.

116
00:07:09,119 --> 00:07:10,679
I heard about Xiaoman

117
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:11,880
and His Highness's incident.

118
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,839
Xiaoman was absent
from the academy today.

119
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,279
I figured something
must have happened.

120
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,559
I came to see

121
00:07:17,799 --> 00:07:19,000
if there's anything I can do to help.

122
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,239
On the day of Xiaoman's wedding,

123
00:07:23,119 --> 00:07:24,760
I sent someone to deliver
a message to you

124
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:25,760
at the brothel.

125
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,799
However, you did not show up.

126
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:30,519
I was unaware of this matter.

127
00:07:30,799 --> 00:07:31,480
Well,

128
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,559
it no longer matters now.

129
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,399
Xiaoman is married now.

130
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,320
Besides, she has a huge
trouble to deal with right now.

131
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:39,720
Zhu Momo came from the capital.

132
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,320
She forbade Xiaoman from
pursuing her studies.

133
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,760
I wanted to take her

134
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,200
to meet Teacher Liu on
the day of examination

135
00:07:45,359 --> 00:07:46,720
and seek help from Teacher Liu.

136
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,799
However, it seems like...

137
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,119
Even Teacher Liu wouldn't
be able to help her.

138
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,359
At this point,

139
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,279
Principal Yang is the only
one that could help her.

140
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,559
On the day of the examination,

141
00:07:56,760 --> 00:07:57,839
try your best to help Xiaoman

142
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,200
take the test at the academy.

143
00:07:59,880 --> 00:08:01,079
I'll submit Xiaoman's test papers

144
00:08:01,079 --> 00:08:02,119
to Principal Yang Chidao.

145
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:05,279
Principal Yang is highly respectable
in Wujiang Prefecture.

146
00:08:06,119 --> 00:08:07,799
Back at the palace,
Commandery Prince of Julu

147
00:08:07,799 --> 00:08:09,160
was tutored by Principal Yang.

148
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,200
In the whole of Wujiang Prefecture,

149
00:08:11,679 --> 00:08:13,399
Principal Yang is the only one who can

150
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,920
control Zhao Xiaoqian.

151
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,839
Leave it to me.

152
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,440
All you have to do is bring
Xiaoman to the academy.

153
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,119
What's the matter?

154
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,600
Nothing.

155
00:08:25,799 --> 00:08:26,760
I shall thank you

156
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,959
on Xiaoman's behalf, Congwen.

157
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:30,399
I'm going to

158
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:31,559
deliver a message to
Commandery Prince's Mansion right now.

159
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:38,860
(Commandery Prince's Mansion)

160
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:42,479
Lady.

161
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:46,440
Since you've

162
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,479
gained His Highness's
grace to return home,

163
00:08:48,679 --> 00:08:50,039
you should enjoy your time there.

164
00:08:50,359 --> 00:08:51,239
I informed

165
00:08:51,239 --> 00:08:52,599
Zhu Momo about this.

166
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:54,559
There's no need for you
to return urgently.

167
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:55,919
Spent some time with your family.

168
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,880
The gifts

169
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,359
are all packed up by Mr. Liangji.

170
00:08:59,359 --> 00:09:00,400
Lady Xie, hurry up.

171
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:01,760
I'm coming.

172
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,840
I'll return as soon as possible.

173
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,479
Lady Xie did not bring
any attendants along.

174
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:22,239
Xie Family will be troubled

175
00:09:22,239 --> 00:09:23,159
to carry the gift on their own.

176
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,679
Tag along and help with the goods.

177
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,080
Yes.

178
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:32,400
Stop the carriage.

179
00:09:36,239 --> 00:09:37,159
Go ahead.

180
00:09:37,919 --> 00:09:39,080
My sister will be waiting for me here.

181
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:40,799
Zhu Momo ordered for us

182
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,400
to send you right to your door step.

183
00:09:43,119 --> 00:09:43,880
Besides, there's a carriage of goods...

184
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:44,479
How about this?

185
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,919
Go ahead and return.

186
00:09:46,599 --> 00:09:48,440
My sister and I are going
to buy some baked bread.

187
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:50,039
It's my father's favourite.

188
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:50,640
After that,

189
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,359
my sister and I will return home
on her carriage.

190
00:09:53,119 --> 00:09:53,559
All right.

191
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,119
I would like some baked bread, too.

192
00:09:56,599 --> 00:09:57,520
You should leave first.

193
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:58,599
After Xiaoman and I are done,

194
00:09:58,599 --> 00:09:59,440
we will come to you.

195
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:01,400
Go on.

196
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,440
My mother could barely wait.

197
00:10:13,239 --> 00:10:13,760
Let's hurry.

198
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:14,559
Otherwise, we wouldn't make it.

199
00:10:15,239 --> 00:10:16,119
You haven't told me

200
00:10:16,119 --> 00:10:17,599
why I should take
the examination at the academy.

201
00:10:17,719 --> 00:10:18,599
It doesn't matter.

202
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:19,719
I'll not cause you harm.

203
00:10:20,799 --> 00:10:21,599
Where's our carriage?

204
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,559
It's arriving soon.

205
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,119
Give it a moment.

206
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:27,260
(Brothel)

207
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:27,599
Get on.

208
00:10:27,599 --> 00:10:28,280
Gnaw on it.

209
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,559
Give it a bite.

210
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,440
Bite on it.

211
00:10:30,719 --> 00:10:31,679
Bite on it.

212
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:32,599
Yes, attack.

213
00:10:32,599 --> 00:10:33,159
Bite it.

214
00:10:33,599 --> 00:10:34,320
Come on.

215
00:10:35,039 --> 00:10:35,719
Zhao Xiaoqian,

216
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,679
what happens if you lose?

217
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,359
It's your call

218
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,559
under one condition.

219
00:10:40,719 --> 00:10:42,479
You're troubling me
with the matters of your family.

220
00:10:42,719 --> 00:10:43,960
You insist to play a bet with me.

221
00:10:44,599 --> 00:10:46,440
If it wasn't for your brother's sake,

222
00:10:47,479 --> 00:10:48,479
I couldn't be bothered.

223
00:10:48,479 --> 00:10:49,200
Shut up.

224
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:50,719
If it wasn't for you,

225
00:10:50,719 --> 00:10:51,799
things wouldn't have ended up this way.

226
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,239
Don't worry though.

227
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,000
I'm one to concede defeat.

228
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,599
Same goes to you.

229
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,479
Attack.

230
00:10:58,479 --> 00:10:59,039
That's right.

231
00:10:59,039 --> 00:10:59,799
Jin Guo, advance.

232
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:01,200
Advance.

233
00:11:01,599 --> 00:11:02,479
Ming Guan.

234
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,840
Good job!

235
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:08,840
Zhao Xiaoqian.

236
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,559
It's your turn

237
00:11:09,799 --> 00:11:10,919
to obey me now.

238
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,479
Come on.

239
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,479
Come on.

240
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,599
Shen Yan.

241
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:26,719
Do not carry this too far.

242
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:28,039
Are you refusing me?

243
00:11:28,719 --> 00:11:29,679
Fine.

244
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,479
The one who said he'd concede defeat

245
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:32,719
wasn't me anyway.

246
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:34,679
Let's go.

247
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:35,960
Hold up.

248
00:11:39,239 --> 00:11:40,039
I concur.

249
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,679
I admit my defeat this time.

250
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:47,840
However, if you failed to

251
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,119
accomplish the task I ordered you to,

252
00:11:49,719 --> 00:11:51,400
the conflict between us
will not be easily

253
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,320
resolved at the racing ground.

254
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:54,719
I know what the old servant of yours

255
00:11:54,719 --> 00:11:55,840
is thinking.

256
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:58,559
She wants to make me your relative.

257
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:00,479
Dream on.

258
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,840
If my sister is married to you,

259
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,400
my name is no longer Shen Yan.

260
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:07,599
Zhao,

261
00:12:07,599 --> 00:12:08,799
what are you doing over there?

262
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:09,960
Hurry up and get ready.

263
00:12:10,599 --> 00:12:11,440
Leave

264
00:12:11,719 --> 00:12:13,239
the rest to me, Master Shen.

265
00:12:27,119 --> 00:12:27,799
We'll see.

266
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,599
Hurry up.

267
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:35,919
We're running out of time.

268
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:36,840
The class is commencing.

269
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,840
We're running late. Hurry.

270
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,280
Hurry.

271
00:12:44,580 --> 00:12:48,460
(Jingnv Pavilion)

272
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:49,559
Xiaoman.

273
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:52,479
Don't worry.

274
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,840
No one would find out.

275
00:12:54,359 --> 00:12:55,760
This is the best solution for now.

276
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:56,760
Don't think about anything else.

277
00:12:56,760 --> 00:12:57,599
Just take the test.

278
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:59,400
Don't worry about the rest.

279
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,320
Leave it to me.

280
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:03,359
We shall head on inside then.

281
00:13:03,359 --> 00:13:03,840
Let's go.

